name: What if... [#3]
description:
... Rembrandt's brother, Rubens Peale, would travel through time and space to be here with us? Against all odds and whatever the consequences?

This project visits classical paintings and gives life to its characters. It is a tribute to the great masters from the past.


[original music composed specifically for this piece by Bruno M. Miranda;
based on "Rubens Peale with a Geranium" by Rembrandt]
